datoCmsKey.name: Chelsie Nectow
datoCmsKey.bio: Chelsie Nectow (she/her) is a queer, NYC based performer and this summer marked ten years in the city! She is a graduate of the Manhattan School of Music. Chelsie also teaches performing arts at the Metropolitan Montessori School where she is developing a social justice theatre program. She loves hanging with her pup, getting out of the city to hike, learning to sew garments, and spending time with her chosen family. Member of AEA.
